      "span_text": "A deletion of DMD exons 3-9 is reported to be associated with a mild BMD phenotype [CITATION_1] , and further investigations on patients with other in-frame deletions in the DMD amino terminal region may help to define better functional dystrophin isoforms that could be induced by AO mediated exon selection.",
